@startuml
title Graderate State Machine

[*] --> Waiting : /waitUntilStartDateArrives

state Waiting
state Active
state Expired
state Archived

Waiting --> Active : startDateReached

Active --> Active : /maintainValidityPeriod
Active --> Expired : finishDateReached

Expired --> Archived : expirationDatePassedOneYear

@enduml
